                            <comment id="117965" author="springiscool" created="Fri, 24 Jul 2015 04:59:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oliver, Christoph&apos;s example pretty much matches the pattern of what my authentication &lt;tt&gt;String&lt;/tt&gt; should look like.  I think using the &lt;tt&gt;&apos;&lt;/tt&gt; to prevent the split should work nicely. Just make sure that it is documented somewhere.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
